Question:::How to create a cmake files(Build, CMakeLists.txt, main.cpp)   manually????? 
Answer:::::create CMakeLists.txt Main.cpp build files in current directory and 
then write these commands

cd build
cmake ..

make
cmake ..
./executablefilename
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
rm -rf ./build/  (to remove build)






