#How to install clang format on linux

1.sudo apt-get install clang-format
2.open vscode file/preference/setting
3.search clang-format
4.In setting search "Clang-Format: Executable" and copy the path there.(path can be find by command "which clang-format".
5.and save it.
6.and also add this path to .vscode/settig.json             "clang-format.executable": "path"

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) add .clang-format file.
2) Make variables private ( Never expose variable in a class unless it's necessary, It means someone from outside can make changes in your objects state which is not necessary)
3) Make accessor functions to access these private variables.
4) Make use of class variables instead of passing means jo hum function definition ma variable usi waqt declare karta han.



